name.long: Fish, cod, Pacific, cooked, dry heat

footnotes.text: Samples were obtained from 12 retail stores using a probability-based sampling plan.  Some fish had been treated during processing to retain moisture on thawing.  Untreated fish = 91 mg sodium/100g.
